snippet.title: This Is The Only Level 3 Walkthrough / Speedrun - 2:57.97 (0 Deaths)
snippet.description:
This is a video of me, Tasselfoot, beating This is the only level 3 in 2:57.97 and not dying.

I have a total of 7-8 seconds of mistakes in the run: lost about 2 seconds on slingshot.  lost half a second on deadly walls afloat.  about 2.5s on multiple elephants (bad mistake).  1s on text-based adventure.  1s on tricky doors.  and maybe .5s on misplaced doors....  but my layout on B.L.U.E. is the best I've ever had, so that saved a ton of time.

Game: http://armorgames.com/play/12745/this-is-the-only-level-3
